Name Rascal/Libraries/Prelude/Set/index
Synopsis Map set elements to a fixed index.
Function map[&T,int] index(set[&T] s)
Usage import Set;
Examples 
rascal>import Set;
ok
rascal>index({"elephant", "zebra", "snake"});
map[str, int]: ("zebra":2,"elephant":1,"snake":0)
